{"tid":558350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"匯豐PayMe推新功能 一年365日均可派利是","createTime":"2018-02-12T07:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T02:14:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":50,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"657712202c313f1fe342828d01dea8ae72ba8aa4","tid":558350,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180212/s00002/52c53da7addddac627ffc3b1c46f091d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180212%2Fs00002%2F52c53da7addddac627ffc3b1c46f091d.png&h=b856cd00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨近新春，各支付平台相繼推出電子利是功能。繼上周八達通O! ePay（好易畀）加入新功能「e利是」後，匯豐銀行旗下PayMe亦宣布新增派電子利是功能。<br />\n<br />\n由即日起，PayMe用戶只需點按利是按鈕，然後發送利是金額，收款人便會收到利是和具個人特色的祝福語。該行更把按鈕設定為永久功能，一年365日均可為親朋好友送上祝福。"},{"pid":"4e5f0bceff01d70b73ca3d8ad4ac8c9ec81b61fa","tid":558350,"uid":154000,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T08:04:54.000Z","msg":"玩到好似微信支付咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb154929bd4872fedd59dd978b5360d80147279","tid":558350,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd301a111e1f3c375db291aa22cebbbe832ed136","tid":558350,"uid":153778,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"101帛金，祝福語：年年有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36adef3816d05472cc876f24feff81aea15142a6","tid":558350,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7363c41fc708b69d9c8dcb0ce924c5cb8307af14","tid":558350,"uid":103127,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc24911bfd3a85c28bec9abf490e97bc8ae8a226","tid":558350,"uid":38173,"like":79,"dislike":7,"score":72,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T08:11:30.